Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:44.94,Main,NANAKO,0,0,0,,Em xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:48.28,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,Thật xin lỗi quá. Con chó nó...
